The higher-ups are the only ones allowed to retain memory of the entire 527-day year. Everyone else is still present and conscious with their memories and experience during the rest of the year, and behaves as would be expected of them during these extra days, including upholding any responsibilities relating to containment. The SCPs are also subjected to this time loss, so it doesn't really give them any advantage.







